<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٥٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(تصم)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> يوم الجمعة إلا أن <span class="c2">(تصوم)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> يومًا قبله أو بعده <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
